WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:02.459
Myocarditis is inflammation of the myocardium, the

00:00:02.459 --> 00:00:04.215
contractile muscle of the heart.

00:00:04.215 --> 00:00:06.673
Global annual incidence ranges from ten to

00:00:06.673 --> 00:00:09.132
twenty-two cases per one hundred thousand, and

00:00:09.132 --> 00:00:11.590
it accounts for up to twelve percent

00:00:11.590 --> 00:00:14.049
of sudden cardiac deaths in adults under

00:00:14.049 --> 00:00:14.400
forty.
